Looks up \fIA\fR and \fIM\fR in \fIP\fR\(cqs mac binding table\[char46] If an entry is found, stores \fB1\fR in the 1-bit subfield \fIR\fR, else 0\[char46]
.IP
\fBExample:\fR \fB
