\fB\fIR\fB = select(\fIN1\fB[=\fIW1\fB], \fIN2\fB[=\fIW2\fB], \[char46]\[char46]\[char46]);\fR
\fBParameters\fR: Integer \fIN1\fR, \fIN2\fR\[char46]\[char46]\[char46], with optional weight \fIW1\fR, \fIW2\fR, \[char46]\[char46]\[char46]
