.SH "SSL TABLE"
.PP
SSL configuration for ovn-sb database access\[char46]
.SS "Summary:
.TQ 3.00in
\fBprivate_key\fR
string
.TQ 3.00in
\fBcertificate\fR
string
.TQ 3.00in
\fBca_cert\fR
string
.TQ 3.00in
\fBbootstrap_ca_cert\fR
boolean
.TQ 3.00in
\fBssl_protocols\fR
string
